{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107360/extras/enter_the_grooveyard.gif?t=1738538651\" /><br><br>Grooveyard is a chill puzzle game brimming with humor and skeletons. Use your magical powers to manipulate walls and guide your skeletal minions to freedom. Enjoy a mix of strategy and rhythm as you uncover the secrets of your bodiless origins.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107360/extras/gameplaygif_shortergif.gif?t=1738538651\" /><br><br>Grooveyard features six unique worlds, each with its own aesthetic and challenges. Start in a traditional graveyard, master wall-jumping in a ruined cathedral, unlock doors in an underground prison, navigate broken tiles in a crystallized cave, and defy gravity in a hellish palace. Finally, test your skills in the ultimate world. Each puzzle offers multiple solutions, rewarding clever and efficient play.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107360/extras/game_features.gif?t=1738538651\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107360/extras/tomb.png?t=1738538651\" />\u00a0\u00a0Over 60 puzzles across six unique worlds with distinct themes.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107360/extras/head.png?t=1738538651\" />\u00a0\u00a0Speak with all your freed skeletons to unravel the mystery of the Grooveyard.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107360/extras/soul.png?t=1738538651\" />\u00a0\u00a0Optimize your solutions to receive higher ratings.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107360/extras/note.png?t=1738538651\" />\u00a0\u00a0Gameplay syncs with the music to c